ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectProtocol of 2014 to the Forced Labour Convention, 1930
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the PROTOCOL OF 2014 TO THE FORCED LABOUR CONVENTION, 1930, adopted at Geneva on June 11, 2014 in order to ratify Convention 81 and Protocol 29 and to ensure respect for fundamental principles and rights at work.
